column26: Ban Amber Heard From Twitter For Misinformation!
column33: Ban Amber Heard From Twitter For Misinformation!
column34: As we all know and saw, Amber Heard lied in her OpEd, on Twitter, and under oath which is against Twitters terms of service saying quote “We define misleading content ('misinformation') as claims that have been confirmed to be false by external, subject-matter experts or include information that is shared in a deceptive or confusing manner. Misleading content that falls under any of the policies above may be subject to one or more of the actions below. This content is identified through a combination of human review and technology, and through partnerships with global third-party experts.” And the way they handle this misinformation is quote “We manage the risk of public harm in many ways. The combination of actions we take are meant to be proportionate to the level of potential harm from that situation. People who repeatedly violate our policies may be subject to temporary or permanent suspensions.” Due to these facts Amber Heard Must be removed from Twitter. Please share this petition to not only help Twitter but hopefully Johnny Depp and the entire world of true victims.
